                a(href ='/') Personal Site!
                br
                br
                | The main purpose of this portfolio is to interest those that are still new to the programming world, to take a chance in Nodejs.  A lot of programmers start with PHP, Ruby on Rails, Django, etc. but Nodejs is truly a fun "hipster" language that I think all developers can truly enjoy.  I wanted to demonstrate its flexibility and allow your imagination create everything else with the technologies I've demonstrated.  At first, it'll be modifying the source code little by little, but once you get the hang of it, you'll be able to deploy applications like THAT!
